{"tid":2494094,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【《黑社會》吹雞】資深演員王鍾病逝本月20日設靈","createTime":"2021-04-18T11:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T22:18:40.000Z","uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"29c21321796d7f6b4368952066601494fde9ccbe","tid":2494094,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210417/photo/bkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001_01p.jpg?20210418030131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210417%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20210418030131&h=52da11e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾拍攝《武狀元蘇乞兒》、《人海孤鴻》以及《凶榜》等電影的資深藝人王鍾（原名姜佩君）日前因病離世，享年74歲，喪禮將於4月20日於紅磡寰宇殯儀館設靈，翌日出殯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210417/photo/bkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001_02p.jpg?20210418030131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210417%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20210418030131&h=0ac4b8cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺《武狀元蘇乞兒》入面，王鍾（中）飾演「莫長老」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210417/photo/bkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001_06p.jpg?20210418030131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210417%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20210418030131&h=63c22693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王鍾被尊稱為寫實警匪片的導演祖師。《黑社會》飾演吹雞<br />\n<br />\n王鍾1969年加入邵氏擔任武師，於70、80年改任演員，曾演出多齣麗的電視警匪劇如《大丈夫》、《大控訴》等，其後再轉拍電影，演出超過70部電影，當中包括與周星馳合作的《武狀元蘇乞兒》；1980年首執導筒，自編自導自演《金手指》，當時更開創了寫實警匪片之先河，亦被尊稱為寫實警匪片的導演祖師。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210417/photo/bkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001_07p.jpg?20210418030131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210417%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20210418030131&h=e2e743b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王鍾，黃霑，周潤發<br />\n<br />\n1990年他淡出電影圈，有指曾移居澳洲，近年回流香港，王鍾的弟弟是藝人王青（大口青），表弟則是姜大偉，姜大偉受訪時，指曾從朋友口中聽到表哥離世的消息，但因已失聯數十年，未能聯絡到其家人：「我哋搵到王鍾姨甥嘅電話，但佢冇覆，可能想低調啦，我都係想睇有乜嘢可以幫手。」姜大偉說跟王鍾小時候感情不俗，住樓上樓下，經常一齊落街玩，是兒時玩伴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210417/bkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210417%2Fbkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001.html&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=1e653ab0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210417/bkn-20210417224602278-0417_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5c90017d9acef1e1e72dbecbc4e23215d2d67113","tid":2494094,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"九點鐘 有骨氣"},{"pid":"38c7eaf420b16888b30a37734caf63280ac016e3","tid":2494094,"uid":35221,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"5c90017d9acef1e1e72dbecbc4e23215d2d67113","tid":2494094,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"九點鐘 有骨氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"八點鐘🤔"},{"pid":"50bf7452eb078c008a4a9e4d66195735d19b1729","tid":2494094,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38c7eaf420b16888b30a37734caf63280ac016e3","tid":2494094,"uid":35221,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"5c90017d9acef1e1e72dbecbc4e23215d2d67113","tid":2494094,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"九點鐘 有骨氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"八點鐘🤔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src